{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f9ca755a-88aa-443a-ab31-ec367effb7d5", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9ca755a-88aa-443a-ab31-ec367effb7d5@3.pkg/1772597480497/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597481111", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9ca755a-88aa-443a-ab31-ec367effb7d5@3.pkg/1772597480497/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597481111"}, "identifier": "f9ca755a-88aa-443a-ab31-ec367effb7d5", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>“理国要道，在于公平正直”意思是治理国家最重要的，在于保持政令、措施的公平与正直；“公与平者，即国之基址也”表明公平是国家的基础，都体现了公平对国家的重要性，①③符合题意；②体现的是爱国主义精神，不符合题意；④体现的是和平，友善相处，不符合题意。故选A。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>公平通常是指人们基于一定标准或原则，处理事情合情合理、不偏不倚的态度或行为方式。下列名言能够体现“公平”的有（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①理国要道，在于公平正直　 ②苟利国家生死以，岂因祸福避趋之</p>\n\n<p>③公与平者，即国之基址也　 ④亲仁善邻，协和万邦</p>\n", "title": "公平通常是指人们基于一定标准或原则，处理事情合情合理、不偏不倚的态度或行为方式。下列名言能够体现“公平”的有（    ）①理国要道，在于公平正直　 ②苟利国家生死以，岂因祸福避趋之③公与平者，即国之基址也　 ④亲仁善邻，协和万邦", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9ca755a-88aa-443a-ab31-ec367effb7d5@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754838483337", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": fa